function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	Hydra.QuestSetCustomParamFromActor(1, idActorSpawned)
	MinimapAddPingForParticipants(idActorSpawned, 10, true)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	local idNPC = T_NPCS[idActorGizmo]
	
	-- handle NPC escape
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idNPC) then
		Hydra.ActorRemoveFromPrefabScopedGroup(idNPC, "EH_Trigger")
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_FREED, idNPC)
	
		if S_ACTOR_GIZMO == GIZMO_STAKE then
			Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idNPC)
		end
		--Sort through runTo positions. If the nearest runTo does not have a path, try the farthest, if that also
		--has no path, just fade and delete.
		if T_FLEE_LOCS ~= nil then 
			table.sort(T_FLEE_LOCS, function(a, b) return Hydra.ActorDistanceSquaredBetweenActors(idNPC, a) < Hydra.ActorDistanceSquaredBetweenActors(idNPC, b) end)
			local idNearestRunTo = T_FLEE_LOCS[1]
			local NEARESTPOS = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(idNearestRunTo)
			local NPCPOS = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(idNPC)
			
			if Hydra.DoesPathExistBetweenPositions(NPCPOS, NEARESTPOS, true) then
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNPC, idNearestRunTo, "NPC_RUN", false, true)
				Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idNPC, 2)
			else
				Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idNPC, 2)
				
			end
		else -- handle non-npc gizmo case
			Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(T_NPCS[idActorGizmo], 2)
			Hydra.ActorKill(idActorGizmo)
		end
	end
	
	-- spawn defenders
	
	ID_LAST_GIZMO_USER = idActorPlayer
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)
	if sLevelAreaName == S_LEVEL_AREA then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("PlayerInLevelArea", idSelf, idSelf)
	end
end

function Start()
	if #Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVEL_AREA) > 0 then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("PlayerInLevelArea", idSelf, idSelf)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorDetector) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActorDetector) then 
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_HELP_BARKS, idActorDetector)
	end

	
end

function Start()
	local sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD

	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD_HEROIC
	end
	
	Events.SpawnRewardChest(CHEST_LOCATION, sChest)
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	for i, enemy in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("EH_Unique")) do
		Hydra.ActorKill(enemy)
	end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	if Hydra.ActorGetMonsterRarity(idActorKilled) == Hydra.MR_SUPER_ELITE then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("SUPER_KILLED", idSelf, idSelf)
	end
end

tHasHeardStartConv = {}
ID_LAST_GIZMO_USER = Hydra.ACDID_INVALID

--tuning / setup knobs
local N_GIZMOS_TO_SPAWN = 6 - Hydra.PrefabScopedActorGroupGetCount("EH_Gizmos")
local T_SPAWNERS_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("EH_Monster_Spawner")
local T_SPAWNERS_ELITE = Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("EH_Elite_Spawner")
local T_SPAWNERS_CHAMPIONS = Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("EH_Champion_Spawner")
local S_ACTORGROUP_GIZMO = "EH_Gizmos"

CHEST_LOCATION = Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("EH_CHEST")[1]
ID_SPAWNER_UNIQUE = Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("EH_Unique_Spawner")[1]

-- spawn normal monsters
local nSpawnerCount = #T_SPAWNERS_MONSTERS
if nSpawnerCount > 0 then
	FYShuffle(T_SPAWNERS_MONSTERS)
	
	for i = 1, nSpawnerCount do
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(T_SPAWNERS_MONSTERS[i])
	end
end

FYShuffle(T_SPAWNERS_ELITE) -- shuffle outside, want the elites spread out here
-- spawn one elite pack
if #T_SPAWNERS_ELITE > 0 then
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(T_SPAWNERS_ELITE[1])
end

-- Once this value is > 1 it'll cause champions to spawn (so world tier 3 and up)
-- subtracting 1 instead of 2 because WTs are index 0 in code (so WT3, 2 in code, produces 1 Champ)
local nChampionCount = Hydra.GameGetCurrentWorldTier() - 1

-- Spawn a champion for each world tier above 2
if nChampionCount > 0 and #T_SPAWNERS_CHAMPIONS >= nChampionCount then
	FYShuffle(T_SPAWNERS_CHAMPIONS)
	
	for i = 1, nChampionCount do
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(T_SPAWNERS_CHAMPIONS[i])
	end
end


FYShuffle(T_GIZMO_SPAWN_LOCS)

T_NPCS = {}

for i=1, N_GIZMOS_TO_SPAWN do
	local ptSpawn = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(T_GIZMO_SPAWN_LOCS[i])
	local ptFacing = Hydra.ActorGetFacing(T_GIZMO_SPAWN_LOCS[i])
	local sActorToSpawn = Hydra.ActorPickFromEncounter(S_ACTOR_GIZMO, idSelf)
	
	if sActorToSpawn == "" then
		sActorToSpawn = S_ACTOR_GIZMO
	end	
	
	local idLastCreatedActor = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(sActorToSpawn, ptSpawn, ptFacing, false, 0, 0)
	
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idLastCreatedActor, S_ACTORGROUP_GIZMO)
	
	if sActorToSpawn == GIZMO_STAKE then -- stakes require the NPCs spawn with different offset than cages
		ptSpawn = Hydra.PositionOffset(ptSpawn, ptFacing, 0.35)
	end
	
	T_NPCS[idLastCreatedActor] = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(Hydra.ActorPickFromEncounter(ENCOUNTER_NPC, idSelf), ptSpawn, ptFacing, false, 0, 0)
	
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(T_NPCS[idLastCreatedActor], "EH_Trigger")
	
	if sActorToSpawn == GIZMO_STAKE then -- stakes require the NPCs adopt sitting neutral animset
		Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(T_NPCS[idLastCreatedActor], ANIMSET_SIT_TIEDUP)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(T_NPCS[idLastCreatedActor], POWER_DESTROY_NEARBY_DEST)
	
end
